            "block_style": "horizontal",
            "icon": "",
            "icon_heading": "",
            "icon_content": "<p>The supplement industry is filled with bold promises, but few brands deliver real transparency or control. In the U.S., dietary supplements are regulated by the FDA  but not before they reach the market. That means many low-quality or even unsafe products can sit on shelves for months before any action is taken.  </p><p>With thousands of new supplements launched each year, most consumers are left in the dark about what they’re really putting in their bodies. At Ancient Bliss, we do things differently because your health should never be a gamble.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        }
      },
