            "block_style": "horizontal",
            "icon": "",
            "icon_heading": "",
            "icon_content": "<p>Every Ancient Bliss supplement is manufactured in an NSF GMP-registered facility, adhering to the highest industry standards. That means you can trust that what’s on the label is exactly what’s in the bottle — nothing more, nothing less.</p><p>  We follow the FDA’s Current Good Manufacturing Practices (cGMP) under CFR Part 111, ensuring each product meets strict guidelines for identity, strength, purity, and composition.<br/>To go even further, our supplements undergo both in-house and third-party testing, so you can feel confident that every capsule is clean, safe, and crafted with integrity.<br/></p>"
          }
