          "type": "content_with_icon",
          "settings": {
            "block_style": "horizontal",
            "icon": "",
            "icon_heading": "",
            "icon_content": "<p>Safety, quality, and transparency are essential — but without real results, they mean nothing. At Ancient Bliss, we don’t just promise purity — we deliver supplements that work.  <br/><br/>Each formula is carefully crafted to support your health with potent, plant-based ingredients backed by indigenous wisdom and validated by science. We use no synthetic fillers — only powerful herbs that honor the integrity of nature and your body. <br/><br/>Our goal is deeper than physical wellness. We guide you toward full-spectrum healing — body, mind, and spirit — so you can make better choices, live more authentically, and reconnect with what truly nourishes you.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        }
      },
